<li>Improve date validation error messages (<code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">54812</code>).</li>
<li>Added documentation for the classes resource (<code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">52734</code>).</li>
<li>Updated descriptions of variables in the Swagger UI to fit the expected values and added JSON Examples to descriptions where needed (<code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">54739</code>).</li>
