<h2 id="v1.5.4-2022-04-27">v1.5.4 (2022-04-27)</h2>
<ul>
<li>The valid date range is now specified (<code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">54668</code>).</li>
<li>A new App Setting was added to configure the amount CPU cores utilized by the UCS@school Kelvin REST API (<code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">54575</code>).</li>
<li>It is now possible to define multiple schools for users via PATCH and PUT requests (<code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">54481</code>, <code class="interpreted-text" role="uv:bug">54690</code>).</li>
</ul>
